      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable workhorse that won't break the bank? This car is in fair condition and ready for its next chapter! While it shows some honest character through noticeable cosmetic wear and has a few mechanical quirks typical of its age, it still runs strong and gets you where you need to go. It\u2019s a fantastic opportunity to own a dependable vehicle at a budget-friendly price!",
