    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2019 Audi A4 Premium Plus in Moonlight Blue Metallic. This vehicle has been a reliable daily driver, kept in a climate-controlled garage and serviced exclusively at authorized dealerships. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, though close inspection reveals minor road peppering on the front bumper consistent with careful highway use. Inside, the Atlas Beige leather remains supple and free of tears, and the cabin is strictly smoke-free. Every feature, from the Virtual Cockpit to the Bang & Olufsen sound system, functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is robust; the 2.0L turbocharged engine pulls smoothly, and the Quattro AWD system provides confidence in all weather. Recent maintenance includes a fresh oil change, new cabin filters, and a multi-point inspection showing healthy brake pad life. Included are two sets of keys, the original owner\u2019s manual, and a complete folder of service receipts. This is a dependable, elegant sedan that balances performance with executive comfort.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
